text.tspan: SETUP: Place all PARKS in squares by agreement
ADJACENT: two squares sharing a side
an opponent's HOVEL or an opponent's HOTEL
NEAR: two squares sharing a side or corner
Place one of your pieces (HOVEL, HOUSE or HOTEL) in an empty square
May not be placed ADJACENT to
No legal moves for either player
1 PENALTY POINT for each GROUP of pieces of their colour
+ 1 for each HOTEL of their colour NEAR 2 HOVELS
+ 2 for each HOTEL of their colour NEAR 3 HOVELS
+ 3 for each HOTEL of their colour NEAR 4 or more HOVELS
Player with fewest PENALTY POINTS WINS
Any two ADJACENT pieces of the same colour are in the same GROUP
